ActiveSupport ‚Äì Important Methods (Cheat Sheet)
1Ô∏è‚É£ Object extensions (Object, NilClass, Blank)
Presence / blank checks ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê
.blank?
.present?
.presence


Examples:

"".blank?        # true
nil.present?     # false
"abc".presence   # "abc"

2Ô∏è‚É£ String extensions
Case & formatting ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê
